  <title>What is a playlist?</title>

  <p>A playlist is a selection of custom-ordered music tracks. It enables
  you to divide your music collection into smaller sets of songs.</p>

  <p>For example, if you want to listen to different version of a particular
  song, no matter who performed it, you can create a playlist for this, and
  listen to those songs in order. You can create a playlist for a party that
  contains only disco music, or love songs, or rock-n-roll.</p>

  <p><app>Rhythmbox</app> supports <link xref="playlists-standard">standard</link> and <link xref="playlists-automatic">automatic</link> playlists.</p>
  
  <note style="tip">
    <p>With some portable music players, you can use the playlists created
    with <app>Rhythmbox</app>.</p>
  </note>

